uh, but I do wish you would let me know how things are going now and then.

Go capture more Pokemon and collect some new badges too!

Hey, Brock, when do you think that eggs going to hatch?
Are you sure it is all right to just take that?

I will raise this one for you.

You mean you sleep with that egg?
It is the only way it will hatch.
So, Brock, what kind of Pokemon's going to hatch out of that thing anyway?
To tell you the truth, Ash, I do not know.
You mean it might even turn out to be a Tentacruel?
I would just love a Tentacruel!
But it could it even be an Aerodactyl?
-I would like it to be a Golem!
Oh, imagine if it were a lovely Lapras.
I cannot wait to see what kind of Pokemon hatches, no matter what it is.
They are hatching a new Pokemon!
Whatever it is, we got to get our hands on that egg.
This could be the chance we been waiting for.
Imagine when the boss hears we have captured a Pokemon!
We have not even succeeded in capturing that one little Pikachu from those kids!
We have a proud tradition of failure to uphold!
I do not believe my eyes!
We kick up our legs so you will buy our eggs!
What kind of Pokemon eggs are they?
Wait and find out when they hatch!
We do not need any Pokemon eggs'because we already have one of our own.
-To unite all peoples within our nation!
-To denounce the evils of truth and love!
-To extend our reach to the stars above!

Is this what you are looking for?
- Eh, we did it! - A great success!
It was because I made such a cute egg salesgirl.
So shall we cook it over easy?
Or maybe we can scramble it?
-We can make a little fried rice! -
You are not cooking it because I am hatching it.
I will warm it with my body.
If I put it down my beautiful egg, it will cool off, and it will not hatch!
Now, my little eggy-weggy, while you and I share a nice hot soak,
I am going to tell you a bath time story.
I told you I am going to hatch it not eat it!
Time for us to go sleepy!
-I never realized Meowth could be so... -Revolting.
If we just follow these eggs, they will lead us all the way to Team Rocket!
Wow, they are pretty dumb, are not they?
Leaving us a trail of broken eggs.
If they are so dumb, how come they are the ones who have the egg?
I guess you have a point there.
Rise and shine, my little eggy-poo!
Meowth's going to make you nice and shiny because we got a lot of incubating to do.
-I told you to lay off the e-g-g-s!
How can you be so insensitive, you numbskull?
Hey, give me back my egg!
And all along, I thought this was our egg.
Go get them and my egg!
It feels like there is something moving inside!
If Pikachu had not caught it...
-But what kind of Pokemon is it?
Hey, now that Dexter's been upgraded, he will know the answer!
Specific information about this Pokemon is still unavailable.
You think so too, do not you, Pikachu?
So now which one of us gets to keep Togepi?
I am the one who incubated the egg.
But I was the one who found it in the first place.
I just let you watch it for a while!
I think I should keep Togepi because it likes me best, right, Togepi?
Togepi has made the right choice.
I found it, so it is mine!
Well, maybe you should have taken better care of it!
-But you never took care of it!
I took care of it more than all of you put together!
You never saw how much Meowth cared for that egg.
They were together when they ate.
They were together when they slept.
Just hearing it brings tears to my eyes.
I never knew you were so sensitive.
All I want from you is my Togepi!
The only way to decide this is with a Pokemon battle!
We will have a tournament, and whoever wins gets to keep Togepi.
-Are you in, or are you out? -
-So we will have a six-way tournament.
These two have no right to participate!
I hereby testify that neither of you performed a single act to assist Togepi.
I cannot believe you are being so selfish!
Then just the four of us will battle!
Let us make it a sudden death battle by using just one Pokemon each.
I do not have any Pokemon to battle with!
Hey, guys, could I borrow one of your Pokemon?
What am I going to do now?
First up is Brock versus Meowth.
-Being your own trainer must be tough.
Meowth is not doing all that badly.
I did not know Meowth was so spunky.
Your scratch attack cannot do anything against Onyx's hard stone body.
But Meowths scratch and bite attacks
are not any good against that giant rock Pokemon!
I will do it for Togepi!
The absolute victory drench with water attack!
I am merely a parent fighting for its child!
And I am going to win this tournament!
Next up is Ash and Misty.
-This time I am going to beat you!
Ah, yes, just as I expected.
You are not allowed to call your Pokemon back!
Okay, aim for Psyducks head, Bulbasaur!
Yeah, like I am that dense!
-Bulbasaur, go lick Psyduck on the head!
You will never lick Psyduck if you lick it.
In that case, I choose Meowth!
I can still remember when you were just an egg,
and all we went through together.
For your sake, Togepi, I, Meowth, will win you back!
I lost so fast, I am a little shocked!
I hope you will be very happy with your new trainer.
I told you, but you did not want to believe me.
Look, it does not want to go to anyone else but me now.
Hey, what is going on here?
Togepi is imprinted with the image of the first thing it sees
after it hatches, thinking this is its mother.
When it hatched, Misty was the first thing it saw!
Togepi likes me, because it thinks I am its mother!
I will love you just like a mother would.
You will help me take care of Togepi, will not you, Pikachu?
Well, with Misty as its new trainer,
it seems like Togepi is the real winner, do not you think?
